    public class MapModuleActivity
extends StorageModuleActivity

    MapModuleActivity

    In the order of ModuleActivities, this one is the fifth module which it handles GoogleMap. It uses Map as an interface and the main job will be done in MapImpl class. Just like StorageModuleActivity this module tries to notify any changes using Rx BehaviorSubject. This time this subject is the LatLng of the center of the screen while camera is in idle state
